<https://w3id.org/ontologies-ULL/OSDi#hasOffsetParameter> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/ontologies-ULL/OSDi#hasOffsetParameter> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <https://w3id.org/ontologies-ULL/OSDi#hasProbabilityDistributionParameter> .
