<https://w3id.org/ontologies-ULL/OSDi#hasProbabilityDistributionParameter> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Defines a parameter of a probability distribution. This is a general property which can be used for any parameter of any probability distribution, but more specific subproperties are provided for the most common parameters (average, variance, lambda, etc.)"@en .
